test(server): add unit tests for storage-json and storage-sqlite

Add 20 test cases covering all three storage modules:
- storage-json.js (15 tests): boardExists, readBoard/writeBoard roundtrip,
  appendLog, ensureLogFile, overwrite, multi-write integrity, large board,
  special characters, corrupted JSON handling
- storage-sqlite.js (3 tests): module loading, NOT_IMPLEMENTED throws,
  interface shape parity with JSON backend
- storage.js factory (2 tests): API shape validation, default backend

All tests use isolated temp directories and follow the project test harness
pattern (passed/failed counters, cleanup in finally block).

Closes #101

